comments: Watanabe (BKN) establishes himself in Oubre Jr.'s (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Plumlee (CHA) contests the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Durant's (BKN) left hand after the release.

Durant (BKN) initiates marginal contact as he places a resting hand to Rozier's (CHA) side during his drive. The contact does not affect his SQBR, or his ability to make the pass to his teammate. Rozier's momentum carries him out of bonds.

Oubre Jr (CHA) engages in some contact as he momentarily places two hands around Watanabe's (BKN) body, but immediately disengages as he releases. The contact is marginal and does not alter Watanabe's FOM.
Watanabe (BKN) establishes himself in Oubre Jr.'s (CHA) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Rozier (CHA) is last to make contact with the ball before it goes out of bounds. BKN correctly maintains possession of the ball.
Oubre Jr (CHA) avoids making more than marginal contact with Durant (BKN) during his shot attempt.
Durant (BKN) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Oubre Jr. (CHA) initiates contact with Thomas' (BKN) arm during the drive and affects Thomas's (BKN) SQBR.
Prior to the inbound, Thomas (BKN) goes to but not through Oubre Jr. (CHA) when they come together and marginal contact occurs.
Rozier (CHA) reaches in and initiates contact with Thomas' (BKN) body during an attempted take foul.
Plumlee (CHA) commits a take foul on Thomas (BKN).
Durant (BKN) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
